\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d056dc835d344c470d939db59cc36afd85796c31","tid":1379103,"uid":198813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:02:37.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5f6d7620cc2229d9d46938de39501f143bcb7d","tid":1379103,"uid":198813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:06:44.000Z","msg":"和解先可以繼續針對政權同警犬去行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分化會有反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34aa15f65cdcca4bcc152c6e317ad9ab8a2f930","tid":1379103,"uid":198813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:08:57.000Z","msg":"We connect!"},{"pid":"0c38c9f191a7f93430d716ea1860ae476bf7113e","tid":1379103,"uid":285320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:25:49.000Z","msg":"要贏，起碼唔可以早過敵人倒下！<br />\n當政府內部，黑警岀現左少少分裂，我地自己都有分裂，入左抗爭嘅樽頸。<br />\n行得到今日，就係本著兄弟爬山，各自努力嘅信念<br />\n團結，堅持落去，直到淋病下台，直到成立獨立調查委員會，直到我地嘅訴求得到回應。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"5460733019adb90d89ecf14d39d04b92894c71a5","tid":1379103,"uid":198813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c38c9f191a7f93430d716ea1860ae476bf7113e","tid":1379103,"uid":285320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:25:49.000Z","msg":"要贏，起碼唔可以早過敵人倒下！<br />\n當政府內部，黑警岀現左少少分裂，我地自己都有分裂，入左抗爭嘅樽頸。<br />\n行得到今日，就係本著兄弟爬山，各自努力嘅信念<br />\n團結，堅持落去，直到淋病下台，直到成立獨立調查委員會，直到我地嘅訴求得到回應。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n香港人加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695cda53fc52d8d7a6b0734803cde03d6722b950","tid":1379103,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:34:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9c45bf2e8b9b33b8ad4915146a5b80d21d7ac8","tid":1379103,"uid":22971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:44:19.000Z","msg":"巴打聽朝再開過post 可能太夜喇"}]}